a", "tag": "counter sink", "note": "Enters with X +1/+1 counters, removes them to deal 1 damage."}, {"name": "Herd Baloth + Counter Engine", "tag": "token flood", "note": "Herd Baloth creates a 4/4 Beast token whenever a +1/+1 counter is placed on it."}, {"name": "Iridescent Hornbeetle", "tag": "insect army", "note": "Whenever one or more +1/+1 counters are placed on a creature you control, create that many 1/1 Insect tokens."}, {"name": "Triumph of the Hordes", "tag": "single-card kill swing", "note": "4-mana sorcery: until end of turn, your creatures get +1/+1, trample, and **infect**."}, {"name": "Toxrill, the Corrosive", "tag": "attrition control finisher", "note": "7-mana 7/7 legendary creature."}], "rulings": [{"name": "Rad counters decay ONLY when nonland cards are milled", "note": "milling a land removes no rad counter, so it persists into the next turn. Fighting that decay with proliferate is the whole engine."}, {"name": "Rad counters hit EVERYONE, including you", "note": "you self-mill and lose life. Morgul-Knife (Shadowspear) lifelink is the built-in offset."}, {"name": "Proliferate adds rad counters to opponents AND +1/+1 counters to your creatures simultaneously", "note": "the central interaction."}, {"name": "The multipliers stack multiplicatively", "note": "Tekuthal doubles all proliferate; Vorinclex MR doubles every counter you place on opponents (Mothman ETB \u2192 2 rad each) and your own placements; Doubling Season doubles counters on your permanents \u2014 including Bloodchief's quest counters, so the combo arms in 2 life-loss triggers, not 3."}, {"name": "Mothman's +1/+1 distribution triggers once per mill event", "note": ", regardless of how many players milled at once."}, {"name": "Mindcrank + Bloodchief is not online the turn Bloodchief lands", "note": "it needs 3 quest counters first (proliferate accelerates this)."}], "composition": [{"name": "Game Changers", "count": 3}, {"name": "Proliferate Sources", "count": 9}, {"name": "Rad Counter /